            <title>[FLINK-16139] Co-location constraints are not reset on task recovery in DefaultScheduler</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-16139</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The colocation constraints are not reset on task recovery, which may lead to task recovery failures when allocating slots.&lt;br/&gt;
